  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody  
      tr
        td(align='left')  
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr 
                td
                  a(href=url, target='_blank') Confirm your email address
  p if you are already registered as a user, please ignore this email!
  p - Ofeimun Mathias, CEO     